law.history: Repealed 1979 (1st Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 2, sec. 10, effective February 10, 1979. -- Amended 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 74, Art. VI, sec. 107(21) and (28). -- Amended 1972 Ky. Acts ch. 256, sec. 8. -- Amended 1964 Ky. Acts ch. 89, sec. 4. -- Created 1962 Ky. Acts ch. 37, sec. 1.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Misrepresentation of fact to obtain assistance -- Action of secretary.
